Beast Comms Manifesto

Communication is not a feature.
It is the substrate of coordination, family, memory, and peace.

When communication fails, everything else begins to fracture.

⸻

The problem

The modern internet does not fail by accident.

It optimizes for:
	•	convenience over sovereignty
	•	abstraction over control
	•	centralization over resilience

Most users cannot:
	•	address each other directly
	•	maintain stable identity at the network layer
