	•	messages move
	•	messages are carried
	•	messages arrive later

This is not degradation.

This is resilience.

⸻

The role of the user

Users are not passive endpoints.

Each device can be:
	•	a sender
	•	a receiver
	•	a courier
	•	a bridge

Participation strengthens the network.

⸻

The outcome

A communication system that:
